body_html:
this issue is caused by the count_nonzero method in svdf mode. there is int64 cast in this method which won't be supported by _slim_android build. the other two models don't use count_nonzero, so they don't have this problem.

after fix the cast int64 issue, you also need to add not_equal op in bazel build. hope it helps.
